data.description: Come visit this spacious 3 bed, 1 bath home on a quiet street in the heart of Wilmington. This home is move-in ready with plenty of room for an owner or investor to add their own touches. You'll be welcomed by a large front porch with plenty of room for furniture. Entering the home, you'll be greeted by a large living room and a first-floor half bath. Coming into the kitchen, you'll notice a significant amount of counter space as well as an eating area in the back room. as well as a recently updated second-floor full bath.  Upstairs, the bedrooms are well-scaled, one bedroom includes a rear bedroom featuring a balcony. The home also has walk-up access to the attic/roof. Schedule your tour today!
